<h2>Some agreements with respect to salsa.debian.org</h2>

<h3>User's roles</h3>

<ul>
  <li>All people asking for access will be granted the Developer role.</li>
  <li>DD's are Master by default.</li>
  <li>DM's can become Master only after they worked on Qt/KDE packages for several months.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Repository layouts</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>qt/</strong> everything from qt.io.</li>
  <li><strong>kde/</strong> frameworks/plasma/apps.</li>
  <li><strong>3rdparty/</strong> non-Qt stuff that needs to be packaged
  because it is used by something packaged (and not already in Debian).</li>
  <li><strong>extras</strong>: everything else.</li>
</ul>
